Package org.lifstools.jmzqc

package org.lifstools.jmzqc
Base package for MzQC Java implementation. Please check the Converter class for methods to read and write MzQC. The MzQC base object is wrapped in a generic Coordinate object. Object bindings were generated using Quicktype and simplified manually.
